		<item>
		<title>WorkSpaces（ユーザー設定）</title>
		<link>https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/archives/119</link>
				<pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2019 16:27:36 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[morihiroaws]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Workspaces]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/?p=119</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[前回は、管理者MorihiroさんがユーザーであるMorihiroさんのためにWorkSpaceを設定してあげ &#8230; <a href="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/archives/119" class="more-link">続きを読む <span class="screen-reader-text">WorkSpaces（ユーザー設定）</span></a>]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>前回は、管理者MorihiroさんがユーザーであるMorihiroさんのためにWorkSpaceを設定してあげる、という操作をやってみました。</p>



<p>今回は、ユーザーであるMorihiroさんがそのWorkSpaceを使い始めるときに行う操作をやってみたいと思います。</p>



<p>管理者Morihiroさんの設定が完了すると、ユーザーのMorihiroさんにメールが届いていました。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-35-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-120" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-35-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-35-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-35-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-35.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>ここに書いてあるとおりに淡々とやるだけですね。まずはメールにかかれているリンクをクリックします。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-36-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-121" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-36-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-36-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-36-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-36.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>ここでユーザー名とメールアドレスと入力して、初期パスワードを設定します。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-38-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-122" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-38-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-38-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-38-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-38.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>なんだかパスワードが設定できないなと思ってよく見たら、パスワードに利用する文字の条件を満たさないといけないみたいです。これを満たすパスワードを設定します。そして「ユーザーの更新」をクリックすると、こんな画面に行きます。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-40-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-123" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-40-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-40-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-40-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-40.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-41-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-124" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-41-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-41-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-41-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-41.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>どうやらWindows用のクライアントソフトをダウンロードしてね、ということのようなので、「Windows Download」をクリックします。そしてソフトをダウンロードしてインストールします。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-43-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-125" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-43-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-43-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-43-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-43.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-45-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-126" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-45-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-45-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-45-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-45.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>クライアントソフトをインストールしたら、自分のPCのデスクトップに、「Amazon　WorkSpaces」というショートカットができました。ここから、東京のどこかのAWSのセンターにつくった、私のパソコンに遠隔操作で接続できるということですね。早速、ショートカットをクリックして接続してみます。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-46-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-127" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-46-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-46-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-46-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-46.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>クリックすると、こんな画面が。。。さっき送られてきたメールに書いてあった、登録コード(Registration Code）」を入れて「Register」をクリックします。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-47-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-128" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-47-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-47-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-47-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-47.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-51-2-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-131" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-51-2-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-51-2-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-51-2-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-51-2.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>多少時間がかかりましたが、自分のPC（外側の青い背景の画面）の中に、遠隔操作で東京のどこかのAWSのセンターにある私のAWS Workspacesの画面が見えるようになりました。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-53-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-132" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-53-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-53-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-53-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-53.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>今回はExcel, Powerpoint, Wordもちゃんと入っています！</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-54-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-134" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-54-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-54-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-54-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-54.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-55-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-135" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-55-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-55-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-55-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-55.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-56-1-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-136" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-56-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-56-1-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-56-1-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-56-1.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>試しにExcelを開いてみますが、ちゃんと開けます。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-59-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-137" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-59-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-59-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-59-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-59.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-60-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-138" srcset="https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-60-1024x576.png 1024w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-60-300x169.png 300w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-60-768x432.png 768w, https://aws.morihiro.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/2019-05-02-60.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p></p>
